commands:

h, help             = show this message
a, att, attack      = you must enter "attack [enemy name] [damage amount]
r, rep, report      = report on the enemies, give their stats
t, turn             = move 1 turn forward (used for decreasing batt capacity mainly)
st, stop            = stop program, abandon progress
s, save             = save all info to file for later retreval (not yet implemented)
n, names            = print all of the names of the enemies